%% Diagram: Payment lifecycle state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: POST /payments
    pending --> requires_action: 3DS2 challenge required
    pending --> requires_capture: Auth only ok (manual capture)
    pending --> processing: Auth+capture in flight
    pending --> failed: Validation / fraud block
    requires_action --> processing: Challenge passed
    requires_action --> failed: Challenge failed / abandoned
    requires_capture --> processing: POST /capture
    requires_capture --> canceled: POST /cancel (release hold)
    requires_capture --> failed: Auth expired (window elapsed)
    processing --> succeeded: Network / issuer approved
    processing --> failed: Network / issuer error or decline
    succeeded --> partially_refunded: POST /refunds (partial)
    succeeded --> refunded: POST /refunds (full)
    partially_refunded --> refunded: Remaining amount refunded
    succeeded --> disputed: charge.dispute.created webhook
    disputed --> succeeded: Dispute won (representment)
    disputed --> refunded: Dispute lost (chargeback)
    refunded --> [*]
    canceled --> [*]
    failed --> [*]
